TUX PICROSS

Manual Installation
-------------------

The following dependencies need to be installed to compile and run tuxpicross:

sdl, sdl_gfx, sdl_image, sdl_ttf, imagemagick

To build tuxpicross, enter the src directory and run

make

To install, run

make install

as root.

By default, tuxpicross will install files in 

/usr/bin/
/usr/share/applications/
/usr/share/tuxpicross/


Installation from AUR (Archlinux)
-------------------

Package Name: tuxpicross
URL: http://aur.archlinux.org/packages.php?ID=35212


Enjoy!
